  "notes": [
    "Pivot Table 是 chart data API 图，前端通过 `buildQueryContext()` 构造 query context，而不是 legacy `/superset/explore_json/`。",
    "当前图的 API root form_data 键名混合了 camelCase 与 snake_case。必须按 control name 原样提交，例如 `groupbyRows`、`groupbyColumns`、`metricsLayout`、`aggregateFunction`、`valueFormat` 是 camelCase，而 `time_grain_sqla`、`date_format`、`currency_format`、`conditional_formatting`、`allow_render_html` 是源码中的真实 root 键。",
    "`metrics` 控件显式带有 `validateNonEmpty`，这是当前图最高置信的必填字段；`groupbyRows` 与 `groupbyColumns` 没有 validator，因此源码层面它们是可选的。",
    "`buildQuery.ts` 会把 `groupbyColumns` 与 `groupbyRows` 合并成 query `columns`，并在 `time_grain_sqla` 存在且列为 temporal 时，把物理列重写成带 `timeGrain` 的 AdhocColumn。",
    "`series_limit_metric`、`metrics[0]` 与 `order_desc` 会共同决定 query `orderby`。这也是 embedding 场景下最敏感的几个 root 字段之一。",
    "`transformProps.ts` 虽然消费了 `tableRenderer`，但当前 controlPanel 没有暴露该控件，而且 `PivotTable.jsx` 最终固定渲染 `TableRenderer`；`tableRenderer` 不应写入 API 模板。",
    "`conditional_formatting` 的值类型来自 `ConditionalFormattingConfig[]`。`getColorFormatters()` 只认 `column`、`operator`、`colorScheme`、`targetValue` 或 `targetValueLeft/targetValueRight` 这几类键。"
  ],
  "metadata_summary": {
    "description": "Used to summarize a set of data by grouping together multiple statistics along two axes. Examples: Sales numbers by region and month, tasks by status and assignee, active users by age and location.",
    "category": "Table",
    "tags": [
      "Additive",
      "Report",
      "Tabular",
      "Featured"
    ]
  },
  "query_compilation": {
    "frontend_builder": "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-pivot-table/src/plugin/buildQuery.ts",
    "query_context_builder": "D:/vsx/sources/superset-6.0.0/superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-core/src/query/buildQueryContext.ts",
    "base_query_effect": "`buildQueryObject()` 会从 raw form_data 提取 `metrics`、`adhoc_filters`、`row_limit`、`series_limit`、`series_limit_metric`、`order_desc` 等字段，形成基础 query object。",
    "pivot_build_query_effect": "`buildQuery.ts` 会把 `groupbyColumns + groupbyRows` 合并为 query `columns`；如列是 temporal physical column 且设置了 `time_grain_sqla`，会重写为带 `timeGrain` 的 SQL AdhocColumn。随后它根据 `series_limit_metric` 或 `metrics[0]` 生成 `orderby`。",
    "frontend_post_processing": "`transformProps.ts` 会把 raw form_data 映射成组件 props，并基于 `date_format` / `time_grain_sqla` 生成 `dateFormatters`，基于 `conditional_formatting` 生成 `metricColorFormatters`。",
    "query_sensitive_fields": [
      "groupbyRows",
      "groupbyColumns",
      "metrics",
      "time_grain_sqla",
      "series_limit_metric",
      "order_desc"
    ]
  },
